  "instructions": [
    "Heat tandoor clay pot over medium heat and add olive oil.",
    "Add lamb cubes and brown all sides until caramelized.",
    "Stir in chopped onion and minced garlic and cook until onion soft.",
    "Mix in tomato paste, allspice, cumin, and coriander and coat the lamb evenly.",
    "Add sliced zucchini and stir for 2 minutes to combine flavors.",
    "Pour in 1 cup water, bring to a gentle simmer, then cover the pot.",
    "Reduce heat to low and let the tagine cook for 60 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Check seasoning, add salt and pepper to taste, and simmer for an additional 10 minutes.",
    "Remove from heat and let rest for 5 minutes before serving.",
    "Garnish with fresh cilantro if desired and serve hot."
  ],
